OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779238995
OL,3,CStarmer to face Commons grilling as
OL,4,CStreeting plans resignation speech
OL,6,FHis noon showdown with the Opposition
OL,7,Fleader is the first since Parliament
OL,8,Freturned after the May elections that
OL,9,Fsaw Labour suffer heavy losses and
OL,10,Fprompted mounting calls for Sir Keir
OL,11,Fto resign.
OL,13,FIt comes after Mr Burnham was
OL,14,Fconfirmed as the party's candidate in
OL,15,Fthe Makerfield by-election, which was
OL,16,Ftriggered by former minister Josh
OL,17,FSimons quitting to open up a path for
OL,18,Fthe Greater Manchester Mayor to return
OL,19,Fto Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779238995
OL,3,CStarmer to face Commons grilling as
OL,4,CStreeting plans resignation speech
OL,6,FIt is understood that the mayor was
OL,7,Fthe only person shortlisted for
OL,8,Fselection by Labour's ruling National
OL,9,FExecutive Committee, bypassing a vote
OL,10,Fby the local party.
OL,12,FThe decision sets up a contest between
OL,13,FMr Burnham and Reform UK's Robert
OL,14,FKenyon, a local plumber who contested
OL,15,Fthe seat for the party in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
