OL,3,CStarmer to face Commons grilling as
OL,4,CStreeting plans resignation speech
OL,6,FIf he returns to Parliament, Mr
OL,7,FBurnham is widely expected to
OL,8,Fchallenge Sir Keir for the Labour
OL,9,Fleadership, but the Prime Minister has
OL,10,Finsisted he will not "walk away" from
OL,11,FDowning Street.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Mr Streeting, who
OL,14,Fcriticised what he claimed was "drift"
OL,15,Fand a lack of direction within
OL,16,FGovernment in a resignation letter
OL,17,Flast week, has also made clear he
OL,18,Fintends to stand in any contest.
OL,26,@rD@VOUrD@`O]vD@`OUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
