CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779238995
OL,3,CStarmer to face Commons grilling as
OL,4,CStreeting plans resignation speech
OL,6,FSir Keir has insisted he is "focused
OL,7,Fon the job" of governing and at a
OL,8,FDowning Street reception for
OL,9,Fhomelessness charities on Tuesday
OL,10,Ftalked up the Government's record on
OL,11,Frenters' rights reforms as an example
OL,12,Fof "ripping up the failed status quo",
OL,13,Favoiding any mention of the turmoil
OL,14,Fengulfing the party in recent days.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Defence Secretary John
OL,17,FHealey warned Labour's "credibility in
OL,18,FGovernment is at stake" in an apparent
OL,19,Frebuke of leadership jockeying among
OL,20,Frivals looking to oust the Prime
OL,21,FMinister.
OL,26,@nD@]OUoD@KO]tD@DOUtD@eO]yD@XOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
