CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1779238995
OL,3,CStarmer to face Commons grilling as
OL,4,CStreeting plans resignation speech
OL,6,F"I don't care about photo ops or PR
OL,7,Ffirms. Politics ` to me ` is not about
OL,8,Fthe individual. People will not
OL,9,Fforgive us if they think we're more
OL,10,Fconcerned about ourselves than we are
OL,11,Fabout them," he said.
OL,13,FBut the unrest continued on Tuesday as
OL,14,Fformer Welsh Labour first minister
OL,15,FMark Drakeford told Channel 4 News Sir
OL,16,FKeir's situation was "irrecoverable"
OL,17,Fand that he would support Mr Burnham
OL,18,Fto be his successor.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]xD@VOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
