OL,3,CStarmer to face Commons grilling as
OL,4,CStreeting plans resignation speech
OL,6,FElsewhere, the mayor said he was
OL,7,F"proud and humbled" to be selected,
OL,8,Fand vowed to ensure the voices of
OL,9,Fpeople in Makerfield were "heard loud
OL,10,Fand clear".
OL,12,FHe has put himself forward as the
OL,13,Fcandidate to "change Labour", using a
OL,14,Fcampaign video to call for a "new path
OL,15,Ffor Britain".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@SO]qD@[OUrD@JO]uD@NOUuD@\O]vD@
OL,26,A^OUwD@LO]
